    "content": "<div><p>One of my all-time talks on <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/TEDxNewYork?__cft__[0]=AZUKeLW-ZtwdZf5e9Kjd_aVUjdoJQX3fK6zMcYODg3z67VdCE71kuILmGT2UmnbUAheBnm8Y46n1Cxrasj7vAfJApE39YoaL60FBoFpTxBujp8AoturWLxiR-pJ1r7XF853xR-Nsejz5huvNeCfp6zbl3BgD9rjo0QF2YDZ0JDy1JTHg0ZvEAlFd0xwTjx8UTU4&__tn__=-]K-R\">TEDxNewYork</a> shows how most keynotes are a nothingburger</p></div><iframe width=\"200\" height=\"113\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/8S0FDjFBj8o?feature=oembed\" frameborder=\"0\" allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share\" allowfullscreen title=\"How to sound smart in your TEDx Talk | Will Stephen | TEDxNewYork\"></iframe><div><p><a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/hashtag/tedtalk?__eep__=6&__cft__[0]=AZUKeLW-ZtwdZf5e9Kjd_aVUjdoJQX3fK6zMcYODg3z67VdCE71kuILmGT2UmnbUAheBnm8Y46n1Cxrasj7vAfJApE39YoaL60FBoFpTxBujp8AoturWLxiR-pJ1r7XF853xR-Nsejz5huvNeCfp6zbl3BgD9rjo0QF2YDZ0JDy1JTHg0ZvEAlFd0xwTjx8UTU4&__tn__=*NK-R\">#TEDTalk</a> <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/hashtag/publicspeaking?__eep__=6&__cft__[0]=AZUKeLW-ZtwdZf5e9Kjd_aVUjdoJQX3fK6zMcYODg3z67VdCE71kuILmGT2UmnbUAheBnm8Y46n1Cxrasj7vAfJApE39YoaL60FBoFpTxBujp8AoturWLxiR-pJ1r7XF853xR-Nsejz5huvNeCfp6zbl3BgD9rjo0QF2YDZ0JDy1JTHg0ZvEAlFd0xwTjx8UTU4&__tn__=*NK-R\">#publicspeaking</a> <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/hashtag/quality?__eep__=6&__cft__[0]=AZUKeLW-ZtwdZf5e9Kjd_aVUjdoJQX3fK6zMcYODg3z67VdCE71kuILmGT2UmnbUAheBnm8Y46n1Cxrasj7vAfJApE39YoaL60FBoFpTxBujp8AoturWLxiR-pJ1r7XF853xR-Nsejz5huvNeCfp6zbl3BgD9rjo0QF2YDZ0JDy1JTHg0ZvEAlFd0xwTjx8UTU4&__tn__=*NK-R\">#quality</a> <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/hashtag/influencermarketing?__eep__=6&__cft__[0]=AZUKeLW-ZtwdZf5e9Kjd_aVUjdoJQX3fK6zMcYODg3z67VdCE71kuILmGT2UmnbUAheBnm8Y46n1Cxrasj7vAfJApE39YoaL60FBoFpTxBujp8AoturWLxiR-pJ1r7XF853xR-Nsejz5huvNeCfp6zbl3BgD9rjo0QF2YDZ0JDy1JTHg0ZvEAlFd0xwTjx8UTU4&__tn__=*NK-R\">#influencermarketing</a></p></div>"
